flowchart TD
    A[x64lens CLI] --> B[Argument parser]
    B --> C{Command}

    C -->|info| D[info command orchestrator]
    C -->|mitigations| M[mitigations command orchestrator]
    C -->|gadgets| FUT1[future gadget command]
    C -->|analyze| FUT2[future full analysis command]

    D --> FM[File mapper]
